Titolo: Freeze!

Anno: 2012

Descrizione: Freeze! is a puzzle video game developed by Frozen Gun Games and released in November 2012 for iOS and Android. 
The game reached the top of the App Store in 61 countries. It received several awards and has downloaded over ten million copies.
The concept and gameplay were developeded by Andreas von Lepel, who designed games for the Commodore 64, Amiga, and Game Boy in the 1980s. The artwork with its dark, atmospheric images was designed by Jonas Schenk.